follow-on cycles needed (out of N70 scope):

  N71-A: wire `gpu_warp_shuffle_xor(v, mask)` →
         `shfl.sync.bfly.b32 %r<dst>, %r<src>, %r<mask>, 0x1f, 0xffffffff;`
         (idx-mode neighbor at compiler/codegen/nvptx_target.hexa L927;
