         PTX_OP_SHFL_SYNC_BFLY_B32). lower_test Case 9 sibling.

  N71-B: extend warp-shuffle to FP64 — `gpu_warp_shuffle_f64`/_xor_f64
         composing 2× `mov.b32 %r_lo/_hi, {%fd_src};` + 2× shfl + 1×
         `mov.b64 %fd_dst, {%r_lo,%r_hi};`. Or auto-dispatch by dst type.

  N71-C: integer `/` binop wiring → `div.s64 %rd<d>, %rd<a>, %rd<b>;`
         (signed) or `div.u64` (unsigned, for the by-32 case where
